<br />
Walter Liedtke, “Rembrandt’s ‘Man in a gorget and plumed cap’ in J. Paul Getty Museum,” Burlington Magazine 137 (1995), p. 460.<br />
<br />
Walter Liedtke in Rembrandt/Not Rembrandt in The Metropolitan Museum of Art:  Aspects of Connoisseurship, exh. cat., New York, Metropolitan Museum of Art, 1995, vol. 2, p. 44, under no. 2.<br />
